<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Membership Agreement</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #000; padding: 60px 80px; background: white; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #000; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .document-title { font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .date { text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555; }
        .info-box { background: #f8f8f8; border: 2px solid #333; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .info-box h3 { margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 200px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-value { flex: 1; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .section-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .section-content { text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        ul { margin-left: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        strong { font-weight: bold; }
        .form-row { margin-top: 30px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
        .form-label { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .form-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-height: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .signature-section { margin-top: 40px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header"><div class="document-title">MEMBERSHIP AGREEMENT</div></div>
    <div class="date">Effective Date: {{date}}</div>
    <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Business Information</h3>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Business Name:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Email:</div><div class="info-value">{{Email}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Phone:</div><div class="info-value">{{Phone}}</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content">
            This Membership Agreement ("Agreement") is between <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> and the Member signing below.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. MEMBERSHIP TERMS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Your membership includes access to classes, facilities, and services as specified in your membership type. Membership automatically renews until canceled.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. BILLING AND PAYMENT</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Membership fees will be charged automatically to your payment method on file. You authorize recurring charges until you cancel your membership with at least 7 days' notice before the next billing date.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. CANCELLATION POLICY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            You may cancel your membership at any time by providing written notice at least 7 days before your next billing date. No refunds will be issued for partial membership periods.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. MEMBER OBLIGATIONS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Members must follow all studio policies, treat staff and other members with respect, and maintain current payment information. Violation of policies may result in membership termination without refund.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            You participate in all activities at your own risk. <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> is not liable for injuries, damages, or losses arising from your participation. See our separate Waiver and Release of Liability for full details.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. GOVERNING LAW</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This Agreement is governed by the laws of <strong>{{Jurisdiction}}</strong>.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Member Name:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Signature:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Date:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>